{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485770/extras/SmartJump.gif?t=1738353492\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Isolated and stranded in the middle of the ocean, Tom will have to rely on his knowledge and show his resourcefulness to make it back home.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">General Knowledge Quiz</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to answer 555 multiple-choice questions on various themes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you make the right choice, you move on to the next question.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you make the wrong choice, you fall into the water.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a checkpoint for each question.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Interface</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A counter records how many times you fall into the water.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A timer displays the hours, minutes and seconds.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Day/night cycle</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between sea and mountains, a blue sky during the day.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At night, stars and auroras.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Note from the developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The difficulty of the questions is quite subjective. It really depends on each person's knowledge but I tried (Hi, I'm Scratch) to find a balance, making sure it's neither too easy nor too difficult. Good luck to everyone!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738353492","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485770/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738353492","capsule_image":"https://shared.ak